      "text": "Nearby friends - ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Nearby friends - ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qwLHaLRWWTwpJfopqqNOo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 63.05926728831719,
      "y": 364.1558401012955,
      "width": 153.71986389160156,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1x",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 778783328,
      "version": 179,
      "versionNonce": 1463938656,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771518564614,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "reqs\ncore entities\nAPI / interface\nhigh lvl design\ndeep dives",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "reqs\ncore entities\nAPI / interface\nhigh lvl design\ndeep dives",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6pbiNwx9TjIC5r2-R2EhX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 324.26171875,
      "y": 365.23480945318573,
      "width": 1359.7191162109375,
      "height": 575,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 836018784,
      "version": 1390,
      "versionNonce": 201080416,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771523086702,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "clarifying questions:\n- what is considered nearby? => 5 miles\n- can i assume that the distance is calculated as the straight-line distance between 2 users?\n    in real life, there could be, for example, a river in between the users, resulting in longer distance travelled\n    => yes reasonable assumption\n- do we need to store location history\n    => yes loc history can be valuable for different purposes such as machine learning\n- can we assume if friend is inactive for more than 10mins, that friend will disappear from the nearby friend list?\n    or should we display the last known location?\n    => can assume that inactive friends will no longer be shown\n- do we need to worry about privacy data laws such as GDPR & CCPA?\n    => no need to worry for now\n\nfunc req:\n- get nearby friends location\n- receive nearby friend's loc update\n- update nearby friend list (whenever there is a change) => subscribe + unsubscribe\n\nnon func req:\n- low latency -> in a sense where i want to know updates fast (<1s)\n- availability >> consistency => generally we want this system to be up & running but occasional data point loss is acceptable\n- eventual consistency => loc data store doesnt need strong consistency, few secs delay in receiving locs in different replicas is acceptable\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "clarifying questions:\n- what is considered nearby? => 5 miles\n- can i assume that the distance is calculated as the straight-line distance between 2 users?\n    in real life, there could be, for example, a river in between the users, resulting in longer distance travelled\n    => yes reasonable assumption\n- do we need to store location history\n    => yes loc history can be valuable for different purposes such as machine learning\n- can we assume if friend is inactive for more than 10mins, that friend will disappear from the nearby friend list?\n    or should we display the last known location?\n    => can assume that inactive friends will no longer be shown\n- do we need to worry about privacy data laws such as GDPR & CCPA?\n    => no need to worry for now\n\nfunc req:\n- get nearby friends location\n- receive nearby friend's loc update\n- update nearby friend list (whenever there is a change) => subscribe + unsubscribe\n\nnon func req:\n- low latency -> in a sense where i want to know updates fast (<1s)\n- availability >> consistency => generally we want this system to be up & running but occasional data point loss is acceptable\n- eventual consistency => loc data store doesnt need strong consistency, few secs delay in receiving locs in different replicas is acceptable\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bbi4iuDZ37ysCrN2W-k2r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 326.1270413840506,
      "y": 196.08132331616957,
      "width": 830.1194458007812,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1475830688,
      "version": 402,
      "versionNonce": 1318020000,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771518575189,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "notes:\nwhy is this designed differently from proximity service?\n    => intuition says that a dynamic locations of friends vs static business locations\n    => loc updated more frequently",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "notes:\nwhy is this designed differently from proximity service?\n    => intuition says that a dynamic locations of friends vs static business locations\n    => loc updated more frequently",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8aaeza8-vWJ77wZ-3DI3M",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 317.74348042013975,
      "y": 931.7500070235487,
      "width": 1242.9990234375,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b20",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2015773600,
      "version": 606,
      "versionNonce": 137177696,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771519407852,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "numbers i have/ assumptions:\n- nearby 5 miles\n- location refresh is 30 seconds => human walking speed 1-2km/ hr, dist. travelled in 30 secs wont make a significant difference\n- on avg 100 mil users, every day\n- concurrent users is 10% of DAU, concurrent users is ~10mil\n- on avg, user has 400 friends, assume all of them use nearby friends feature\n- app displays 20 nearby friends per page & may laod more nearby friends upon request\n\n\nBOE estimation:\n100 mil DAU\n10 mil concurrent users\nQPS = 10mil / 30 secs (update happens every 30 secs) => ~300k QPS/ secs",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "numbers i have/ assumptions:\n- nearby 5 miles\n- location refresh is 30 seconds => human walking speed 1-2km/ hr, dist. travelled in 30 secs wont make a significant difference\n- on avg 100 mil users, every day\n- concurrent users is 10% of DAU, concurrent users is ~10mil\n- on avg, user has 400 friends, assume all of them use nearby friends feature\n- app displays 20 nearby friends per page & may laod more nearby friends upon request\n\n\nBOE estimation:\n100 mil DAU\n10 mil concurrent users\nQPS = 10mil / 30 secs (update happens every 30 secs) => ~300k QPS/ secs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
